}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== This device was probably never released by [[D-Link]].
Models are specified as DW-650, WL-650, SOHO-WL16P, [[W-Link WEN-2010]] (OEM) and [[Planex GW-NS11S]] (OEM) in the FCC test report.
"8WLNIC012A1" and "MADE IN TAIWAN" or some similar text is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. This device was manufactured by [[D-Link]]'s manufacturing arm before it split off into [[Alpha Networks]].
